{"type":"message","id":"e88b6715","parentId":"6d2fb909","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:29:38.135Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已关闭所有标签页。浏览器现在是干净的状态。\n\n**为什么会打开这么多标签页？**\n每次我调用 `browser.open` 时，如果浏览器没有正确复用现有标签，就会创建新标签。加上我多次尝试搜索\"刘教户外\"，导致重复打开。\n\n**优化建议：**\n1. **使用 `targetId` 复用标签** - 以后我会先获取标签列表，然后复用现有标签而不是创建新的\n2. **减少重复操作** - 搜索时一次性输入完整关键词，避免多次尝试\n3. **关闭不需要的标签** - 完成任务后及时关闭\n\n现在浏览器已清理干净，可以重新开始操作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"xiaomi","model":"mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":60939,"output":145,"cacheRead":60834,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121918,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774877374825,"responseId":"msg_4f0908e0f4944a9cba693704"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b75a035","parentId":"e88b6715","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:31:13.372Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-03-30 21:31 GMT+8] 使用 targetId 复用标签 这个优化方法你记在哪个文件了"}],"timestamp":1774877473364}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8c8ce4a","parentId":"0b75a035","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:31:14.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_22253f4c42fa45cba22b05f2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"targetId 复用标签 浏览器优化"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"xiaomi","model":"mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":61169,"output":31,"cacheRead":60938,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122138,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774877473368,"responseId":"msg_575b66bc8e504b8ca2f05a02"}}
