{"type":"message","id":"383e3a72","parentId":"17306d93","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:31:16.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d66f3d96d9364a26abebb851","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/tianting/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"xiaomi","model":"mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":61243,"output":30,"cacheRead":61168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774877475262,"responseId":"msg_e847aebfef2b4bdca43801cd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cedf489","parentId":"383e3a72","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:31:16.710Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d66f3d96d9364a26abebb851","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\n\n## What Goes Here\n\nThings like:\n\n- Camera names and locations\n- SSH hosts and aliases\n- Preferred voices for TTS\n- Speaker/room names\n- Device nicknames\n- Anything environment-specific\n\n## Examples\n\n```markdown\n### Cameras\n\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\n\n### SSH\n\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\n\n### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n```\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774877476706}}
{"type":"message","id":"be1782d5","parentId":"1cedf489","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:31:20.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9447e238f4d74760bde4ca55","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/tianting/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md","oldText":"### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n```\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.","newText":"### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n\n### Browser\n\n- **优化方法**: 使用 `targetId` 复用标签，避免重复打开\n- **操作流程**:\n  1. 先调用 `browser.tabs` 获取当前标签列表\n  2. 选择合适的 `targetId` 复用现有标签\n  3. 避免重复调用 `browser.open` 创建新标签\n- **清理方法**: 完成任务后关闭不需要的标签页\n```\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"xiaomi","model":"mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":61499,"output":295,"cacheRead":60508,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122302,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774877476712,"responseId":"msg_1f9cb212fafa473594b321b6"}}
